{"tid":2215864,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發］民陣料警方抗疫為由，向10.1 大遊行發出反對通知書！","createTime":"2020-09-24T09:25:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T10:37:41.000Z","uid":219007,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1d28bd32d5c732cf04d008570b3a66b043b56e4b","tid":2215864,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:25:28.000Z","msg":"【十一遊行】民陣料警方以抗疫為由反對  慨歎現今香港可悲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RVgZSwi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRVgZSwi.jpg&h=f52a7ba4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民陣計劃在10月1日發起遊行，向警方申請不反對通知書，今日 (24日) 民陣與警方商討「十一遊行」後見記者，表示預料警方會以配合政府政策及抗疫為由，向申請發出反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n召集人岑子杰指，今時今日市民的權利全由警方操控，警方會由任何理由及難題阻止召集團體舉行活動，及阻止市民表達訊求，例如要求申請人提出建議，及保證活動不會違反「四人限聚令」。他又表示香港人已有近九個月沒有享有一個合法遊行，形容為香港的可悲。<br />\n<br />\n他亦呼籲市民無論參與與否，務必要顧及自身安危，因警方由政府實施限聚令開始，便以此作為無理拘捕的理由。回看以往警方的手法，經常以大圍捕地、無差別地，在街上見到人便發告票。<br />\n<br />\n攝/ 本台採訪記者<br />\n========================= <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/117540932243292/posts/650665715597475/?extid=IZ6SLJnjsKWohjO3&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F117540932243292%2Fposts%2F650665715597475%2F%3Fextid%3DIZ6SLJnjsKWohjO3%26d%3Dn&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFPhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=998a6579\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/117540932243292/posts/650665715597475/?extid=IZ6SLJnjsKWohjO3&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"b4ac2918206dc545b86f23420cfc11992b73d4bd","tid":2215864,"uid":264326,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:26:18.000Z","msg":"嗯<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hd8aeK3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHd8aeK3.jpg&h=0a20e2a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3ee5f0f19cc931436ba7d7ff5a3de03dbadb330","tid":2215864,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:43:38.000Z","msg":"十月一大定千奇唔好行街"},{"pid":"418cea52b094ec047d05c55e6de9e4a1e6c27a02","tid":2215864,"uid":100581,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:44:52.000Z","msg":"唔批正常<br />\n佢批先驚"},{"pid":"a882aae0b1856de939418052cf627d96d0aba8a4","tid":2215864,"uid":70771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:44:57.000Z","msg":"10月1一定唔會出街慶祝國慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ec83ba9b244fd823140790cd6b232decefbf88","tid":2215864,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ce0f67b8d8b0d3529999a431eef09896f4d425","tid":2215864,"uid":222524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:31:53.000Z","msg":"有咩咁突發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee86778563a1f6814121b829176ed2bd737ee5f1","tid":2215864,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:32:59.000Z","msg":"到時應該同71差唔多"},{"pid":"c381a574c3b220bbbd32bbf0b432a97148e1c428","tid":2215864,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:35:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a09cd2c60fb738b97f87ad377b99a801ad94c4e1","tid":2215864,"uid":74182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"56ce0f67b8d8b0d3529999a431eef09896f4d425","tid":2215864,"uid":222524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:31:53.000Z","msg":"有咩咁突發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:37:41.000Z","msg":"佢會批先係新聞"}]}